arts.ttl: KNVB Cup: Twente survive scare as AZ defeats Groningen
arts.sum: The KNVB Cup continued on Tuesday with FC Twente and AZ Alkmaar amongst the sides in action. Katwijk 2-3 Twente FC Twente defeated a spirited Katwijk side to safely reach the last 16. The Eredivisie side almost scored immediately but Daan Rots hit the crossbar after being sent in on goal.
